        <p>
          "Our latest album titled <em>#LoveCintaMahabbah</em> is special to us first because we feel that we didn't leave anything behind&hellip; meaning, we brought all our past, the good, the not-so-good&hellip; all of it with us! But if you ask me, the sweetness of our latest album lies in between the tracks&hellip; literally and figuratively speaking," said Erwan.</p>

        <p>
          "Not leaving anything behind is one thing&hellip; we've also tried to put in our present as much as we could. Many of our friends from the music side and also a dear friend from the academic side didn't hesitate to respond to our invitation to be featured in our latest album," said Adib.</p>

        <p>
          And both Erwan and Adib agree that, although now they are not as young in age as before, but this chapter of their journey has just begun&hellip; and they hope to invite as many as possible to come and join them! InsyaAllah.</p>

        <hr>

        <p class="author">Erwan Taib &amp; Adib Nahar</p>
      </article>

      <article lang="ms">
